{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304790/extras/slogan_store_asset.png?t=1692869014\" /><br>Based in claustrophobic small maps, with reactive and fast paced movement, PROJECT CHAOS boasts a lack of lengthy death timers, transporting you back into the fight instantly, keeping the momentum of the game rolling.<br><br>Deaths and kills are not recorded and displayed, in favour of a score based system, where bonuses and also detriments can increase or decrease the score. With the goal of the game to obtain the highest score as either a team or a solo player.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304790/extras/gamemodes_store_asset.png?t=1692869014\" /><br>Jump into chaotic battles with Project Chaos signature mode: Chaos. Where with each life you spawn with a completely different loadout. Use the constant changes to learn new weapons, experiment with different playstyles or just enjoy the bonkers mess the gamemode produces.<br><br>Or for the more classic players, jump into the normal Team Death Match and Free For All gamemodes, where you can use your pre-set loadout in an attempt to cause as much chaos as physically possible.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304790/extras/weapons_store_asset.png?t=1692869014\" /><br>You can only cause so much chaos with a stick, so Project Chaos only the provides the most powerful weapons for players to wield.<br>With options like:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Smart Rocket Launchers,<br></li><li>.50 Cal Snipers, <br></li><li>Miniguns, <br></li><li>Lightning SMG\u2019s,<br></li><li>Full Auto Incendiary Shotguns,<br></li><li>and much more make up the in game arsenal.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Win!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2304790/5035a14191151660a